Package: SeuratExplorer
Title: An Interactive R Shiny Application for Exploring scRNA-seq Data Processed in Seurat
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person("Yongchao", "Zhang", , "zhangyongchao@nibs.ac.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c("https://github.com/fentouxungui"))
Description: A simple, one-command package which runs an interactive shiny dashboard capable of common visualizations for single cell RNA-seq. The application requires a processed Seurat object, saved as 'rds' or 'qs2' file.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
